    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "After the refactor, I simplified the custom pollset implementation to only have a global shutdown method.  \r\n\r\nBefore, there was also an individual pollset shutdown function that was only used when running the c-core libuv tests that would spin the loop to make sure all callbacks were run.\r\n\r\nAfter the refactor, I switched the global shutdown to spin the libuv loop until there were no active/referenced uv objects.\r\n \r\n```#ifdef GRPC_UV_HOLD_LOOP```\r\nis only defined for the c-core tests.\r\n"
  },
