    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@nicolasnoble Shall we skip a Node release in 1.11?  I am concerned about a rushed release after deeper fixes in core without going to a proper QA process. The next branch cut (1.12) is April 23 and 1.12 is planned to be released on May 7.  I am partial to skipping Node 1.11 and going with a release from the head of 1.11 as is without this PR. What do you think?"
