    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I'm convinced this is the right approach, and actually reduces the number of kludges we had for running-c-core-with-libuv vs actual node stuff.\r\n\r\nNote all the instances of\r\n```if (grpc_pollset_work_run_loop)```\r\nin this file:\r\nhttps://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/v1.10.x/src/core/lib/iomgr/pollset_uv.cc\r\n\r\nFurthermore, in v1.10.x, ASAN builds fail, specifically in ```grpc_pollset_destroy``` with a heap-use-after free.\r\n"
